<h1 tabindex="-1">WebGPU 的新变化 (Chrome 121)</h1><devsite-feature-tooltip ack-key="AckCollectionsBookmarkTooltipDismiss" analytics-category="Site-Wide Custom Events" analytics-action-show="Callout Profile displayed" analytics-action-close="Callout Profile dismissed" analytics-label="Create Collection Callout" dismiss-button="true" dismiss-button-text="关闭" close-button-text="知道了">
